---
/**
 * Story Section - Narrative Arc Component
 * Inspired by Brainers storytelling approach
 * Flow: Problem → Solution → Proof
 */
---

<section id="story" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#0a0a0f]" data-section>
  <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
  <div class="py-24 lg:py-32 relative">
    <!-- Background glow -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 section-bg">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#ff3366]/5 rounded-full blur-[200px]"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid pattern -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.5) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.5) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>

    <div class="container relative z-10">
      <!-- Section indicator -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff3366] animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[#ff3366] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">PROBLEM_DETECTED</span>
        </div>
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff3366]/50 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <!-- Text content -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight" data-animate="glitch">
            <span class="text-[#9090a8]">כולם מדברים על </span>
            <span class="text-[#ff3366]" style="text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.5);">AI</span>
            <br />
            <span class="text-[#f5f5fa]">אבל מעטים יודעים</span>
            <br />
            <span class="text-[#f5f5fa]">מה לעשות איתו</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-[#c0c0d0]" data-animate="stagger">
            <p class="font-mono" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#ff3366]">></span> ארגונים משקיעים מיליונים בכלי AI מתקדמים
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#ff3366]">></span> אבל העובדים לא יודעים איך להשתמש בהם
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#ff3366]">></span> התוצאה? בזבוז משאבים, תסכול, ופער הולך וגדל
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Warning panel -->
          <div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-[#ff3366]/5 border border-[#ff3366]/30 rounded-xl" data-animate="neon-pulse" data-delay="0.3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center border border-[#ff3366]/50 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#ff3366]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono text-base font-semibold text-[#ff3366] mb-2">WARNING: COMPETITIVE_GAP</div>
                <p class="text-[#d0d0e0] text-base">ארגונים שלא יאמצו AI בצורה נכונה יישארו מאחור. השאלה היא לא "אם" אלא "מתי".</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Visual element - Data visualization -->
        <div class="relative" data-animate="terminal" data-delay="0.2">
          <div class="relative bg-[#12121a] border border-[#2a2a3a] p-8 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Terminal header -->
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-3 bg-[#0a0a0f] border-b border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-t-2xl">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#ff3366]"></span>
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#ffff00]"></span>
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#a855f7]"></span>
              </div>
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] md:text-xs font-medium text-[#ff3366] tracking-wider">MARKET_ANALYSIS.log</span>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-8 space-y-6">
              <!-- Stat bars -->
              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-2">
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-[#b0b0c0]">ADOPTION_RATE</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[#ff3366]">23%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-2 bg-[#1a1a24] overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="h-full w-[23%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff3366] to-[#ff3366]/50" style="box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.5);"></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-2">
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-[#b0b0c0]">SKILL_GAP</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[#ff3366]">67%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-2 bg-[#1a1a24] overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="h-full w-[67%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff3366] to-[#ff3366]/50" style="box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.5);"></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mb-2">
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-[#b0b0c0]">RESOURCE_WASTE</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[#ff3366]">45%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-2 bg-[#1a1a24] overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="h-full w-[45%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff3366] to-[#ff3366]/50" style="box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 51, 102, 0.5);"></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="pt-4 border-t border-[#2a2a3a]">
                <p class="font-mono text-sm text-[#c0c0d0]">
                  <span class="text-[#ff3366]">//</span> רק 23% מהארגונים מצליחים לממש את פוטנציאל ה-AI שלהם
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-[#ff3366]/30"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#ff3366]/30"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Transition line -->
  <div class="relative h-32">
    <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-[#ff3366] via-[#a855f7] to-[#a855f7]"></div>
    <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-[#a855f7] rotate-45" style="box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5);"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- THE SOLUTION -->
  <div class="py-24 lg:py-32 relative">
    <!-- Background glow -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-1/4 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-[#a855f7]/5 rounded-full blur-[200px]"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid pattern -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>

    <div class="container relative z-10">
      <!-- Section indicator -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#a855f7] animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[#a855f7] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">SOLUTION_FOUND</span>
        </div>
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#a855f7]/50 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <!-- Visual element first on desktop - Character Image -->
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative flex items-center justify-center" data-animate="scale-up">
          <!-- Glow effect behind character -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-[#a855f7]/15 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Character image with fade edges -->
          <div class="relative">
            <img
              src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dfudxxzlj/image/upload/v1770417795/0616a06c-820e-4c75-89fd-3f92a1159877_ndhfnn.png"
              alt="חבובוט - הבוט החכם של Focus AI"
              class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[500px] h-auto chavobot-fade"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text content -->
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight" data-animate="slide-left">
            <span class="text-[#f5f5fa]">אנחנו לא</span>
            <br />
            <span class="text-[#9090a8]">מלמדים תיאוריה</span>
            <br />
            <span class="text-[#a855f7]" style="text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5);">אנחנו בונים</span>
            <br />
            <span class="text-[#a855f7]" style="text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5);">יכולות</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-[#c0c0d0]" data-animate="stagger" data-delay="0.2">
            <p class="font-mono" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#a855f7]">></span> צוות המרצים שלנו עובד עם AI בשטח, כל יום
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#a855f7]">></span> ההכשרות נבנות סביב אתגרים אמיתיים
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono" data-line>
              <span class="text-[#a855f7]">></span> תצאו עם כלים שעובדים - לא רק ידע
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Success panel -->
          <div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-[#a855f7]/5 border border-[#a855f7]/30 rounded-xl" data-animate="neon-pulse" data-delay="0.4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center border border-[#a855f7]/50 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#a855f7]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-mono text-base font-semibold text-[#a855f7] mb-2">STATUS: MISSION_READY</div>
                <p class="text-[#d0d0e0] text-base">
                  <span class="text-[#f5f5fa] font-semibold">אצלנו הפוקוס הוא עליך.</span> אנחנו כאן כדי להפוך אתכם לאנשי מקצוע ב-AI - לא למכור לכם עוד הכשרה.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .chavobot-fade {
    mask-image: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      transparent 0%,
      black 8%,
      black 85%,
      transparent 100%
    ),
    linear-gradient(
      to right,
      transparent 0%,
      black 5%,
      black 95%,
      transparent 100%
    );
    mask-composite: intersect;
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      transparent 0%,
      black 8%,
      black 85%,
      transparent 100%
    ),
    linear-gradient(
      to right,
      transparent 0%,
      black 5%,
      black 95%,
      transparent 100%
    );
    -webkit-mask-composite: source-in;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3));
  }
</style>
